-a9ec-3cfb65190000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯需要延长停火，但拒绝付出代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/hamas-needed-to-prolong-the-cease-fire-but-refused-to-pay-the-price/0000018c-2c42-db3a-a1be-3ddf319d0000</link><description>在尝试与以色列谈判取得进展但失败后，哈马斯恢复了火箭发射 ■ 当以色列国防军为加沙长期战斗做准备时，拜登政府警告以色列的国际信用即将耗尽</description><pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 03:56:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/hamas-needed-to-prolong-the-cease-fire-but-refused-to-pay-the-price/0000018c-2c42-db3a-a1be-3ddf319d0000</guid></item><item><title>两名巴勒斯坦人在西岸的不同事件中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-killed-in-separate-incidents-in-west-bank/0000018c-2c46-dc03-a9ec-3c7f2a760000</link><description>《国土报》获得的视频显示，定居者（其中一些人戴着面具）与以色列士兵一起站在约旦河西岸一个村庄被烧毁的房屋附近，几小时后在该村庄发现了一具男子的尸体。在另一起事件中，一名 14 岁巴勒斯坦人在纳布卢斯附近被士兵开枪打死，据士兵称，他拔出一把刀向他们走去</description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 22:09:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-03/ty-article/.premium/two-palestinians-killed-in-separate-incidents-in-west-bank/0000018c-2c46-dc03-a9ec-3c7f2a760000</guid></item><item><title>在与哈马斯的交易中释放以色列阿拉伯囚犯发出了危险的信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/freeing-israeli-arab-prisoners-in-deals-with-hamas-sends-a-dangerous-message/0000018c-2b77-db3a-a1be-3fff6cf10000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 02 Dec 2023 21:49:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/freeing-israeli-arab-prisoners-in-deals-with-hamas-sends-a-dangerous-message/0000018c-2b77-db3a-a1be-3fff6cf10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列背弃人质转而摧毁加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-has-turned-its-back-on-the-hostages-in-favor-of-destroying-gaza/0000018c-2b75-d5f2-a5cc-6f752fec0000</lin